OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FPrime Minister, Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,8,Fcalled on Reform UK to sack its
OL,9,Fhousing spokesman after he said the
OL,10,FGrenfell Tower fire was a "tragedy"
OL,11,Fbut that "everyone dies in the end".
OL,13,FSimon Dudley, a former executive at
OL,14,FHomes England, said the pendulum had
OL,15,F"swung too far the wrong way" on
OL,16,Fregulation after the deadly blaze at
OL,17,Fthe west London tower block in 2017.
OL,26,@rD@[OUrD@cO]sD@JOUsD@cO]wD@AOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FThe Grenfell Inquiry found that the 72
OL,8,Fdeaths were avoidable and had been
OL,9,Fpreceded by "decades of failure" by
OL,10,Fgovernments and the building industry
OL,11,Fto act on the dangers of flammable
OL,12,Fmaterials on high-rise buildings.
OL,14,FDudley was appointed as housing
OL,15,Fspokesman for Reform last month, and
OL,16,Fthe party said at the time he would
OL,17,Flead an urgent review into "Britain's
OL,18,Fbuilding crisis" that would set out
OL,19,Freforms to planning, housing delivery
OL,20,Fand national infrastructure.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@`O]yD@\OUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FIn an interview with Inside Housing,
OL,8,Fpublished on Wednesday, Dudley said
OL,9,Fthe Grenfell fire was a "tragedy" but
OL,10,Fsaid he does not believe the
OL,11,Fregulatory regime is proportionate.
OL,13,FHe went on to say: "Sadly, you know,
OL,14,Feveryone dies in the end. It's just
OL,15,Fhow you go, right?"
OL,26,@qD@YOUqD@aO]uD@TOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FThe Building Safety Regulator, which
OL,8,Fwas set up after the fire and is
OL,9,Fresponsible for regulating the safe
OL,10,Fdesign, construction and occupation of
OL,11,Fhigher-risk buildings, has faced
OL,12,Fcriticism for delays in its approval
OL,13,Fprocesses.
OL,15,FIn June last year, the government
OL,16,Fannounced reforms to tackle delays to
OL,17,Fbuilding new high-rise homes,
OL,18,Fincluding a fast-track process and
OL,19,Finvestment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FHe added: "Extracting Grenfell from
OL,8,Fthe statistics, actually, people dying
OL,9,Fin house fires is rare... many, many
OL,10,Fmore people die on the roads driving
OL,11,Fcars, but we're not making cars
OL,12,Fillegal, so why are we stopping houses
OL,13,Fbeing built?"
OL,15,FHe argued that "You can't stop tragic
OL,16,Fthings happening. You can try to
OL,17,Fminimise excesses, but bad things do
OL,18,Fhappen."
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@MO]wD@POUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FThe effect of poor regulation, he
OL,8,Fsaid, is that it stops houses being
OL,9,Fbuilt.
OL,11,F"So the pendulum has just swung too
OL,12,Ffar the wrong way," he said.
