OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FIn a statement, the Grenfell Next of
OL,8,FKin group said: "The death of our
OL,9,Fparents, partners, children, siblings
OL,10,Fgrandparents and grandchildren in the
OL,11,Fmost horrific circumstances was gross
OL,12,Fnegligent manslaughter, NOT fate.
OL,14,F"Dudley and Reform must apologise to
OL,15,Fthe Grenfell Next of Kin families."
OL,17,FLabelling Dudley's comments as
OL,18,F"shameful", the Prime Minister, Sir
OL,19,FKeir Starmer, called on Nigel Farage
OL,20,Fto sack Dudley.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FJoining these calls, the Housing
OL,8,FSecretary Steve Reed said: "If Nigel
OL,9,FFarage has an ounce of decency, he
OL,10,Fwill sack his housing chief
OL,11,Fimmediately."
OL,13,F"These disgraceful comments about
OL,14,Fthose who died in the Grenfell Tower
OL,15,Ffire are beyond the pale and it is
OL,16,Fcompletely untenable for Simon Dudley
OL,17,Fto continue in his position.
OL,26,@pD@\OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FGreen Party MP Sian Berry said:
OL,8,F"Reform has sunk to a new low and
OL,9,Fshown a real disrespect to the victims
OL,10,Fof Grenfell.
OL,12,F"Anyone who has any awareness of what
OL,13,FGrenfell residents went through, in
OL,14,Ffact anyone with any empathy or
OL,15,Fhumanity, will find these comments
OL,16,Ftruly abhorrent.
OL,18,FNigel Farage must sack Simon Dudley
OL,19,Ffor this disgusting outburst."
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FThe Mayor of London Sadiq Khan
OL,8,Fdescribed Dudley's words as
OL,9,F"sickeningly insensitive."
OL,11,FHe added: "Not an ounce of decency,
OL,12,Fcompassion or respect for the 72 lives
OL,13,Flost and wider community. But this
OL,14,Fisn't a slip-up or a stumble. This is
OL,15,FReform showing us exactly who they
OL,16,Fare."
OL,18,FA Reform UK spokesman said: "Homes
OL,19,Fmust, of course, be built safely.
OL,26,@zD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,F"However, overly burdensome building
OL,8,Fsafety regulations can stifle
OL,9,Fhousebuilding, meaning targets are
OL,10,Fmissed, and the waiting list for homes
OL,11,Fgrows longer at a time when we need
OL,12,Fmore.
OL,14,F"Simon's comments on Grenfell
OL,15,Freflected his broader point that the
OL,16,Fregulatory pendulum has swung too far
OL,17,Fin response to the tragedy.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,F"As he explained, there is a fine
OL,8,Fbalance between overregulation ` which
OL,9,Fcan slow the delivery of new homes `
OL,10,Fand ensuring that more homes are built
OL,11,Fsafely without too much red tape."
OL,13,FGrenfell United, which represents some
OL,14,Fbereaved and survivors, described the
OL,15,Fcomments as "deeply dehumanising".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@bO]wD@MOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FIn a statement on Thursday it wrote:
OL,8,F"Our loved ones did not simply 'die.'
OL,9,FThey were failed. They were trapped in
OL,10,Ftheir homes, in a building that should
OL,11,Fhave been safe, in a fire that should
OL,12,Fnever have happened. Reducing their
OL,13,Fdeaths to an inevitability strips away
OL,14,Fthe truth: this was preventable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775142710
OL,3,CPM urges Farage to sack Reform housing
OL,4,Cspokesman over 'shameful' Grenfell
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,F"To speak about Grenfell in this way
OL,8,Fis to erase responsibility. It
OL,9,Fsuggests this was just fate, just 'how
OL,10,Fit goes,' rather than the result of
OL,11,Fyears of ignored warnings, poor
OL,12,Fdecisions, and a failure to value the
OL,13,Flives of residents, and is deeply
OL,14,Foffensive and ill-informed.
OL,16,F"Everyone deserves the right to a safe
OL,17,Fhome. But this attitude clearly shows
OL,18,FSimon Dudley is not the man to ensure
OL,19,Fthat happens."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
